## PHASE 0 ‚Äî Foundations & safety (do FIRST; cheap insurance, unblocks all the rest)

**1. Staging + separate test DB** (was 5)
Learn how preview/staging works; stand up a Supabase **branch or second project** for testing
payments + new features so nothing is tested against live prod. *This unblocks safe testing of
every later item.* ‚Üí ties to `6(left)‚Ä¶` A1. Deps: none. Effort: M.

**2. Deployment pipeline** (was 4)
Learn how to ship Next.js: Vercel vs Coolify vs your own app server; how the app code and API
routes deploy together (Next.js API routes deploy WITH the app ‚Äî they're not a separate server);
preview deploys per branch; env-var management. Pick one host and document the deploy. Deps: none
(pairs with #1's previews). Effort: M.

> **+ 0a ‚Äî CI gate.** Tests exist (114, money-path libs); still missing: Playwright (5 flows)
> once #1 exists, and wiring `tsc`+`lint`+`vitest` into GitHub Actions. Plan in `6(left)‚Ä¶` A2.
> **+ 0b ‚Äî Observability.** Sentry (client+server) + a real log backend before launch, so
> prod failures are visible.

